{
  "stem": "8725.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And soon after the, like, four soldiers came, and they were-- selecting the color, and they were painting and this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was sitting like Mother Goose on the eggs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was scared to-- to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister did go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, I living by the diner, in the big-- in, in the--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Till I moved to the villa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there, I did have-- right by the diner was a little room for ceremonies, I guess, and I did have that room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, when you're with my sister, about a few days, maybe a week after my sister left, the, the-- Rokita, hey, where is your sister, they ask me?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, he was mad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And just like from nowhere, I say, well, she did have tuberculosis and was sent-- and he turned white, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Just popped out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see how God sometimes puts this-- I said, she did have a tuberculosis, and the major thought that it is-- she had to send her, because that is very infectious.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he did not bother me anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was with him now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I am moving to the villas, right away, because the major said, look, you will serve only dinner.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want you to overlook the painting and the cleaning and this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schultz brought me a little cot for sleeping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He brought-- and he went back and forth with the car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He brought me-- so you don't need to run, he brought me towels, and he brought me to heat my water, and brought some cookies and bread and fruit.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He say that you-- when you get hungry, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so there was-- at night, Major did not move yet, because he wanted everything be cleaned and this.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
